circumstances: Ben Whitehead was reported missing after failing to return Home from the tutoring center, where he had been meeting a friend for help with schoolwork. A colleague, Garry Jones, assisted authorities in searching, leading them to 25 Southside Road, Inverness, IV2 3BG, where Ben was safely found.
q_3_explanation: Ben is 16 years old and may be more vulnerable due to his age.
q_17_explanation: His failure to return home is unusual behavior for him.
q_20_explanation: He intended to meet a friend but failed to return home after.
